    public class Assignment
extends java.lang.Object

    Assignment contains a name, a weight, a gradeType, and a set of statistics along with methods to change these fields

        Constructor for an assignment.
        Parameters:
        name - name of the assignment to be created.
        percentOfCategory - weight of the assignment based on percentage from its parent category.
        maxPoints - maximum number of points each student can get on that assignment.
        dueDate - the date that the assignment is due.
        gScheme - the grading scheme that would be used for this assignment.
        latePolicy - the late policy defined for this assignment.
        hasElectronicTurnin - if the assignment should be turned in electronically or not.
